{"tid":1942983,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【連蝕兩年】廣告收入跌22% TVB去年蝕2.95億元","createTime":"2020-03-25T11:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T17:49:42.000Z","uid":89595,"like":82,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"e11357e133f34ae085d70f0af085e089fd9c5f10","tid":1942983,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:19:08.000Z","msg":"電視廣播（0511）（TVB）公布2019年度全年業績，因為需要就星美債券投資作進一步減值3.3億元，股東應佔虧損達2.95億元，較去年同期增加48.24%。不過撇除有關債券投資減值的話，股東應佔虧損為3500萬元。期內該集團的除息稅、折舊及攤銷前盈利（EBITDA）則達4.61億元，按年大減41.05%。每股派末期息0.2元，按年減少71.43%。<br />\n<br />\n期內TVB在港的廣告收入按年減少22%至只有19.1億元。反而OTT業務方面，來自myTV SUPER及大台網的收入則按告增長17%至5.71億元。香港電視廣播業務本身則由盈轉虧，虧損達3.03億元。<br />\n<br />\n感謝黃心凌及一眾巴打手足狙擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd4004a8f0477c5ed84